name: Prologue: CryptoFlowerz Aerial Seed Drop 01
description:
Aerial Seeding is a method used for planting on farms.  In the MeadowVerse, the process can also be used to grow the CryptoFlowerz Garden.

This motion artwork designed by Victoria Fard commemorates the birth of CryptoFlowerz and celebrates the community around the project. The crystal blue rose is an early rendering from the 2,500 piece collection.

This airdrop was sent to Seed Card holders for the CryptoFlowerz Generative NFT project on January 28th 2022  http://cryptoflowerz.io http://victoriafard.com
